definitions.definition: Belonging to you; of you; related to you (singular; one owner).
examples: Let’s meet tomorrow at your convenience.

definitions.definition: Belonging to you; of you; related to you (plural; more owners).
A determiner that conveys familiarity and mutual knowledge of the modified noun.
examples: Not your average Tom, Dick and Harry.

definitions.definition: That; the specified (usually used with a human referent)
examples: Your man just bought a new car.
Have you seen what your one over there is doing?
